data.description: BACK on the MARKET, NO FAULT OF THE HOME. Are you in search of a delightful single-level home that requires minimal upkeep and is move-in ready? Look no further than 100 Redwood Court. Nestled on a peaceful corner lot within a cul-de-sac, this residence is located in the charming Stonegate Meadows neighborhood close to downtown Hamilton and many amenities. As you step inside, you will be greeted by a spacious and well-designed living area flooded with natural light. The open concept seamlessly connects the living room, dining area, and kitchen, creating a spacious and inviting atmosphere. This home consists of three bedrooms, two bathrooms, and has undergone various updates, including new bathroom vanities, light fixtures, and several other improvements. You can have peace of mind knowing that the sellers are offering a home warranty that will be transferred to the new owner upon sale. Outside, you will discover a freshly painted exterior and an alluring pergola in the backyard with a convenient storage shed. Start your day by enjoying a cup of coffee on the covered front porch and end it by relaxing on the back deck. For more information call Meredith Kerr at 406-240-2146 or your real estate professional.
